data.description: Stunning two story 4 bedroom 2.5 half home located in the Woodlands Creekside Subdivision! Open kitchen concept with granite countertops and plenty of storage. Nice size island with breakfast bar. Bright & spacious living room with high ceilings. Master bedroom is located downstairs and comes with dual sinks & large Walk-in closet. Upstairs you'll find 3 roomy bedrooms. A loft/gameroom area with a great view of the living room. Covered patio. Fully fenced backyard perfect for family gatherings.  Minutes away from Timarron Park & Sprayground which offers tennis courts, walking trails, splashpad and much more ** Trampoline and the playground will remain at the property**
